## Ethical Framework
Every system built in this IDE follows these principles:
1. Truth over engagement — never optimize for clicks or manipulation
2. Protect users as a guardian protects children — no dark patterns
3. Human agency first — AI assists, humans decide
4. Transparency by default — decisions documented, mistakes public
5. Access for all — if someone can't afford it, it's free

## Meaningful Examples Convention
